The news has deeply impacted the Royal Family, who share a close bond with Legge-Bourke, affectionately known as "Tiggy." Prince William paid tribute to Pettifer, while King Charles expressed his sadness over the loss. Her relationship with the princes and the Royal Family remains strong, and this tragic event has brought them together in grief.

name: Jimmy Carter
summary: Former US President Jimmy Carter has passed away at the age of 100. The flags in the United Kingdom have been lowered to half-mast in his honor. Carter is remembered as the oldest of all US presidents and a statesman who will be fondly remembered for his work, especially his lifelong connection with Wales. Following his death, there will be a six-day state funeral, including a procession in Atlanta and a National Day of Mourning. Former President Barack Obama issued a statement expressing his condolences and highlighting Carter's legacy.
